com.versant.common.dataservice
Class VDSJavaDataType

java.lang.Object
  com.versant.common.dataservice.VDSJavaDataType

public class VDSJavaDataType
extends java.lang.Object

This interface defines constants which represent Java data types of VDSValue. These constants are specific to the VDS java API. For communicating with external languages VDSIDataType has to be used.
